uc berkeley x google area 120

summary

For this project, we worked with Google's area 120 and answered the question: What are current perceptions of the creator economy ecosystem among BIPOC creators?

team members

I worked with ian, bea, and eileen on this project. We partnered with an advisor at Google to guide our research.

process
recruitment

Our recruitment was done through personal networks as well as posting flyers the bay, LA, & DC

diary studies

We conducted diary studies over 5 days, comprised of a morning and afternoon survey to learn about how creators were meeting their content creation goals for the day.

interviews

We interviewed 9 participants over zoom to understand in more detail the experience of a BIPOC content creators.
